About Us

With over two decades of experience, ProEvents & Promotions Pvt. Ltd. redefines the event landscape across India and the UAE. Headquartered in Mohali with in‑house fabrication units in Delhi and Chandigarh, we specialise in conceptualising, designing and executing events of all scales. From elaborate corporate conferences to dazzling concerts and immersive exhibitions, our 1,000+ successful events speak to our dedication and creativity.

We believe in delivering quality at your price. Our mission is to combine innovation, meticulous planning and deep market insight to bring your vision to life. Our values centre on client satisfaction, operational excellence, transparency and sustainability.
